Package org.soulwing.prospecto.api.converter

Class PropertyExtractingValueTypeConverter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.soulwing.prospecto.api.converter.PropertyExtractingValueTypeConverter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    ValueTypeConverter
    public class PropertyExtractingValueTypeConverter
extends Object
implements ValueTypeConverter
    A converter that extracts a single String, Number, Boolean, Enum, or Date property from a model object.

    This type converter deliberately excludes information from the view representation that would be needed to reconstruct an instance of the corresponding model object. Therefore, the ValueTypeConverter.toModelValue(Object, ViewContext) method of this converter always returns undefined value; this means that a view node that uses this converter will never be used to update the corresponding model property.

    Author:
    Carl Harris
